Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.92,0:00:11.23,Show Title,,0,0,0,,{\fs142.5\fnGallow Tree\4aFF\pos(443.949,598.286)}KAMEN RIDER
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.04,0:00:15.03,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Shocker is coming,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.69,0:00:18.69,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,with its armies straight from hell
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.31,0:00:22.89,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Their black shadows threaten us all
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.89,0:00:26.53,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,but I'll fight to maintain\Nthe peace of our world!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.53,0:00:30.21,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Go! Go! Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.21,0:00:33.46,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,With my shining machine...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.88,0:00:36.32,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Rider Jump!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.58,0:00:40.10,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Rider Kick!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.15,0:00:44.81,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider, Kamen Rider
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.81,0:00:48.48,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Rider, Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.48,0:00:50.98,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Rider Jump!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.98,0:00:54.69,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Rider Kick!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.61,0:00:59.21,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider, Kamen Rider
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.21,0:01:02.70,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Rider, Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.72,0:01:11.31,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Hongo Takeshi is the\NKamen Rider, a cyborg.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.31,0:01:15.33,Narrator,,0,0,0,,He was modified by the evil Shocker, a secret\Norganization plotting world domination.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.33,0:01:18.82,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider has pledged to fight\NShocker and free humanity!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.97,0:01:24.94,NEP AND TITLE,,0,0,0,,{\fscx100\fs135\bord0\fnCienfuegos\4aFF\b1\pos(487.167,140.389)}The Terrifying Unidogma
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.97,0:01:24.94,NEP AND TITLE,,0,0,0,,{\fscx100\fs155\bord0\fnCienfuegos\4aFF\b1\pos(457.167,710.389)}+ Ghost Monsters
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.88,0:01:38.20,Default,,0,0,0,,What was that flash?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.78,0:01:41.10,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a parachute!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.10,0:01:43.12,Default,,0,0,0,,It's heading for the\Ngraveyard outside town!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.40,0:01:54.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I was sure this was the place...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.38,0:02:00.71,Default,,0,0,0,,It's flashing!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.71,0:02:01.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Over there!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.68,0:02:07.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Here it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.74,0:02:12.63,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, get to work!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.47,0:02:34.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.67,0:02:40.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder what they buried...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.92,0:03:01.20,Default,,0,0,0,,A sea urchin monster!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.16,0:03:03.36,Default,,0,0,0,,It's alive!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.57,0:03:09.80,Default,,0,0,0,,You've seen the great Unidogma...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.80,0:03:11.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I cannot let you live!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.30,0:03:12.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Someone help!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.52,0:03:15.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Help!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.14,0:03:18.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Good.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.14,0:03:22.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Mom! Dad!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.95,0:03:24.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I saw a sea urchin\Nmonster in the graveyard!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.37,0:03:27.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Dad?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.39,0:03:30.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Dad!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.78,0:03:37.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Dad is...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.26,0:03:40.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Mom! Mom!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.18,0:03:44.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Mom is, too...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.84,0:03:50.72,Default,,0,0,0,,That should take care\Nof the whole village.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.72,0:03:52.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Go and count them up.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.76,0:03:53.90,Default,,0,0,0,,That voice...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.90,0:03:55.22,Default,,0,0,0,,They're coming this way!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.22,0:04:03.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Kunihiro Ikeda and his wife, Tokie.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.66,0:04:06.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Their son Kunio isn't here.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.32,0:04:10.01,Default,,0,0,0,,That boy, eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.01,0:04:11.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Find him!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.90,0:04:12.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Fools!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.58,0:04:16.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't make such a fuss\Nover one little child.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.08,0:04:23.82,Default,,0,0,0,,The most important thing now\Nis to make more and more Unidogmas.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.27,0:04:28.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't let a single person\Nenter that village.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.70,0:04:33.96,Default,,0,0,0,,And if anyone does enter...\Ndo not let them leave!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.47,0:04:39.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Boy, the air really is better out here.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.60,0:04:41.40,Default,,0,0,0,,No sign of Shocker, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.40,0:04:42.90,Default,,0,0,0,,It's been a while since\Nwe could relax like this!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.90,0:04:44.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't relax too much.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.14,0:04:46.04,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll be heading home\Nafter we pay our respects.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.04,0:04:47.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.23,0:04:48.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't be like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.24,0:04:50.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Shocker's not going to wait around\Nwhile I'm visiting a few graves.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.52,0:04:53.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, let's get going.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.74,0:04:54.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.39,0:05:00.48,Default,,0,0,0,,- It should be right up here.\N- Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.12,0:05:29.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Tachibana Tobei!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.36,0:05:30.18,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.18,0:05:31.77,Default,,0,0,0,,What's he doing in this village?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.77,0:05:34.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Has he caught wind\Nof our plan somehow?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.66,0:05:37.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Counter-soldiers,\Nfinish off Tachibana Tobei!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.22,0:05:38.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Be patient!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.22,0:05:41.48,Default,,0,0,0,,We can finish him off any time.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.07,0:05:44.36,Default,,0,0,0,,We must deal with Tachibana carefully,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.36,0:05:46.30,Default,,0,0,0,,or we might spur Kamen Rider to action.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.92,0:05:49.81,Default,,0,0,0,,As long as he doesn't catch on, let him go.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.04,0:05:52.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Continue your surveillance.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.12,0:05:59.54,Sign,,0,0,0,,{\an9\fs50\3c&H291808&\bord4}Tachibana Family Grave
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.88,0:06:04.15,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a pretty creepy graveyard...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.76,0:06:07.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't say that, or a ghost\Nmight just haunt you!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.57,0:06:09.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop that! Chairman, you meanie!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.57,0:06:12.57,Default,,0,0,0,,A ghost!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.02,0:06:17.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, don't scare us like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.51,0:06:19.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Help me, mister!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.34,0:06:22.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Help you? What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.16,0:06:25.46,Default,,0,0,0,,My mom and dad... everyone\Nin the town has been killed!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.86,0:06:29.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Killed? Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.73,0:06:32.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Could you tell us the whole story?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.12,0:06:33.98,Default,,0,0,0,,We might be able to help.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.98,0:06:34.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.78,0:06:36.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Just calm down.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.17,0:06:39.92,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you mean, your parents\Nand the townspeople were killed?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.08,0:06:51.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on! Hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.25,0:06:54.48,Default,,0,0,0,,It's right here.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.69,0:07:03.25,Default,,0,0,0,,They were killed!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.06,0:07:07.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Kunio.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.40,0:07:09.37,Default,,0,0,0,,You need to study,\Nnot play around all the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.94,0:07:12.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Can we help you?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.28,0:07:13.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, well...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.44,0:07:15.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Your son said the strangest thing...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.91,0:07:18.25,Default,,0,0,0,,He said you'd been killed.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.25,0:07:20.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Kunio, are you lying again?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.46,0:07:23.80,Default,,0,0,0,,He's really quite a problem child.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.80,0:07:25.44,Default,,0,0,0,,No! That's not my dad!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.44,0:07:26.80,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not my mom!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.80,0:07:28.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Kunio! Enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.84,0:07:29.98,Default,,0,0,0,,This is all nonsense.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.98,0:07:31.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go, Chairman.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.40,0:07:33.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, we'll be going.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.25,0:07:35.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait! Please believe me!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.04,0:07:36.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Kunio!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.81,0:07:37.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Kunio!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.36,0:07:42.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Excuse us.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.15,0:07:54.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Code number zero here.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.18,0:07:55.18,Default,,0,0,0,,HQ, over.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.54,0:07:56.82,Italics,,0,0,0,,HQ, over.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.65,0:08:00.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, Chairman? HQ here.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.05,0:08:01.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.52,0:08:02.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.50,0:08:08.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Pops. Was it nice being\Nback in your hometown?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.13,0:08:12.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I feel refreshed. 2Z4.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.33,0:08:14.46,Default,,0,0,0,,2Z4?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.46,0:08:15.51,Default,,0,0,0,,2Z4?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.82,0:08:17.97,Default,,0,0,0,,2Z4... is that a code?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.28,0:08:29.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm leaving the village now.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.81,0:08:32.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I should make it to Tokyo\Naround seven o'clock.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.88,0:08:35.15,Default,,0,0,0,,That fool, Tachibana...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.15,0:08:37.25,Default,,0,0,0,,He's leaving the village\Nnone the wiser!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.08,0:08:51.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Chairman?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.30,0:08:54.89,Default,,0,0,0,,What child would ever lie\Nabout his parents being killed?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.44,0:08:58.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Then you think the parents\Nwe saw were... you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.90,0:09:01.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to find out what\Nthose "ghosts" really were.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.43,0:09:04.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Who are you people?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.55,0:09:07.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Who are we, you ask?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.78,0:09:21.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Help!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.45,0:09:23.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me go!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.78,0:09:29.32,Default,,0,0,0,,This village is under Shocker's control.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.32,0:09:34.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Its people are being used to create\Nmore and more Unidogmas.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.97,0:09:36.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Shocker?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.54,0:09:37.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Behold...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.79,0:09:41.12,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a Unidogma egg in\Nthe process of hatching.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.12,0:09:45.07,Default,,0,0,0,,If we feed it this child's\Ncells, it will be complete.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.07,0:09:46.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.34,0:09:49.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Help! Someone help!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.40,0:09:52.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Help! Someone!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.86,0:09:54.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Help!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.86,0:09:56.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Help!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.47,0:09:58.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Someone help!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.11,0:10:00.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Yokko.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.62,0:10:01.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Tachibana!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.00,0:10:03.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I knew it...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.51,0:10:05.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Shocker was behind those ghosts!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.44,0:10:06.44,Default,,0,0,0,,- Run!\N- Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.58,0:10:12.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Get them!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.58,0:10:25.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Pops's message contained the code 2Z4.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.21,0:10:26.79,Default,,0,0,0,,"I've located Shocker."
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.16,0:10:28.40,Default,,0,0,0,,But that's some rotten luck...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.40,0:10:31.53,Default,,0,0,0,,running into Shocker when\Nhe goes home to pay his respects.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.53,0:10:33.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe it's all about his attitude.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.44,0:10:35.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, let's hurry.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.32,0:10:42.32,Default,,0,0,0,,What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.50,0:10:51.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Is this the Shocker monster?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.27,0:10:52.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Taki.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.11,0:10:55.35,Default,,0,0,0,,If the monster is here, then only\Ncombatants are holding Otake Village.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.35,0:10:57.60,Default,,0,0,0,,That means I can handle it myself. \NI'll help the Chairman and Yokko.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.60,0:10:58.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.62,0:11:06.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Where are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.82,0:11:27.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Show yourself, new Shocker monster!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.04,0:11:29.52,Italics,,0,0,0,,If you want to see me, come find me!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.73,0:11:39.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Rider Transformation!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.55,0:12:14.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Shocker cyborg...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.88,0:12:16.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Am I?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.70,0:12:18.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that what I look like?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.12,0:12:21.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.70,0:12:26.13,Default,,0,0,0,,The Shocker cyborg you're\Nsearching for is Unidogma...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.13,0:12:28.34,Default,,0,0,0,,He's in Otake Village.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.34,0:12:29.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Unidogma...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.89,0:12:32.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, what are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.96,0:12:34.83,Default,,0,0,0,,What indeed?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.83,0:12:37.41,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll learn what I am soon enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.79,0:12:46.34,Default,,0,0,0,,If Unidogma is in Otake Village,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.34,0:12:48.10,Default,,0,0,0,,that means Taki and Pops are in danger.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.10,0:12:55.90,Bumper Episode 70-98,,0,0,0,,{\blur1\fs90\c&HE4EBE4&\pos(320,534)}KAMEN RIDER
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.96,0:13:04.02,Default,,0,0,0,,It's Taki!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.66,0:13:06.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Taki has arrived!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.60,0:13:07.81,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.57,0:13:10.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Good...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.12,0:13:12.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Seal off all entrances to the village!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.12,0:13:17.64,Default,,0,0,0,,If that brat Taki is here,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.40,0:13:21.15,Default,,0,0,0,,that means Hongo Takeshi...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.68,0:13:23.72,Default,,0,0,0,,the Kamen Rider will come soon!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.38,0:13:26.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone, take your positions!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.82,0:13:29.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.11,0:13:32.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Be patient, Ambassador Hell.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.27,0:13:35.28,Default,,0,0,0,,My leader.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.72,0:13:41.63,Default,,0,0,0,,But if the Kamen Rider arrives,\Nhe'll threaten our plans!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.63,0:13:43.62,Default,,0,0,0,,The Kamen Rider will not arrive.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.54,0:13:47.04,Default,,0,0,0,,What did you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.04,0:13:48.88,Default,,0,0,0,,What exactly do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.37,0:13:52.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Listen only to my orders.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.26,0:13:54.41,Default,,0,0,0,,The Kamen Rider will not arrive.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.41,0:13:58.27,Default,,0,0,0,,You can finish off Shocker's\Nenemies at your leisure.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.19,0:14:02.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-Yes, sir...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.80,0:14:29.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Is this the place?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.91,0:14:39.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Chairman!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.90,0:14:40.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Taki?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.77,0:14:42.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Calm down, you guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.16,0:14:44.91,Default,,0,0,0,,The Shocker monster isn't\Nin the village anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.91,0:14:45.92,Default,,0,0,0,,You mean it?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.92,0:14:47.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Open the door!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.92,0:14:54.05,Default,,0,0,0,,You're sure the monster's gone?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.05,0:14:55.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Hongo's holding it off.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.87,0:14:56.93,Default,,0,0,0,,It's all small fry here.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.93,0:14:57.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, come on out.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.98,0:14:59.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't that great, Kunio?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.16,0:15:01.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Who's this kid?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.40,0:15:02.67,Default,,0,0,0,,A witness to Shocker's plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.88,0:15:04.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Please avenge my mom and dad!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.12,0:15:06.24,Default,,0,0,0,,You mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.58,0:15:08.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Unidogma killed them.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.66,0:15:10.94,Default,,0,0,0,,All right...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.94,0:15:14.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I hereby appoint you to the\NShocker-fighting Kamen Rider Kid Corps.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.26,0:15:15.54,Default,,0,0,0,,You mean it?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.74,0:15:18.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Captain, I'll show you the way!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.42,0:15:19.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Great.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.20,0:15:21.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's blow this joint, then!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.39,0:15:23.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I think I prefer Tokyo anyway!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.38,0:15:24.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.98,0:15:32.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Go that way!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.80,0:15:42.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Taki and Tachibana\Nare heading for area B1F.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.81,0:15:51.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.44,0:15:53.95,Default,,0,0,0,,This road isn't safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.95,0:15:55.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Go that way, then!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.27,0:15:56.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.38,0:16:02.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Direction changed to area B1R.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.14,0:16:19.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn... they're trying\Nto keep us trapped here.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.38,0:16:22.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Kunio, is there no other way?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.59,0:16:24.81,Default,,0,0,0,,You can go through the graveyard\Nand across the mountain!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.81,0:16:25.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Great!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.08,0:16:35.62,Default,,0,0,0,,They're heading just where\Nwe want them to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.60,0:16:39.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Hongo Takeshi!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.92,0:16:44.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm right here!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.16,0:16:55.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Talk! Where are you sending them?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.26,0:16:56.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Well?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.80,0:17:03.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I see... you're sending\Nthem to the graveyard?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.66,0:17:12.50,Default,,0,0,0,,It's creeping me out that\Nwe haven't seen any combatants.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.50,0:17:13.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I feel the same way.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.52,0:17:15.48,Default,,0,0,0,,But it's better that\Nwe don't run into any...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.84,0:17:16.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Hold on!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.06,0:17:30.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey... you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.26,0:17:31.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.46,0:17:32.79,Default,,0,0,0,,- Be careful!\N- Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.64,0:17:41.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Finally... Shocker combatants!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.90,0:17:57.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Monster!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.05,0:17:58.84,Default,,0,0,0,,That was a dirty trick...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.86,0:18:02.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Silence!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.66,0:18:08.36,Default,,0,0,0,,To create more Unidogmas,\Nwe need living humans.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.62,0:18:09.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Unidogmas?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.10,0:18:17.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't let you eat us.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.03,0:18:18.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Listen to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.45,0:18:20.48,Default,,0,0,0,,By feeding them human cells,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.48,0:18:22.58,Default,,0,0,0,,we'll produce more\Nand more Unidogmas.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.58,0:18:25.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I will make Japan into\Na nest for Unidogmas!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.18,0:18:27.12,Default,,0,0,0,,So you're going to eat\Neveryone in the country?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.12,0:18:28.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.64,0:18:30.22,Default,,0,0,0,,First the boy,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.22,0:18:31.82,Default,,0,0,0,,then the woman.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.90,0:18:39.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Hongo!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.78,0:18:41.19,Default,,0,0,0,,You wretch...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.42,0:18:53.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Unidogma, I won't\Nlet you create a successor.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.90,0:18:55.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Silence. Get him!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.68,0:19:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Pops, run!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.30,0:19:01.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.50,0:19:17.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.56,0:19:25.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn you...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.12,0:19:45.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Rider Transformation!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.64,0:20:51.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Dogma Fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.36,0:20:59.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Rider Punch!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.85,0:19:38.58,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Shocker is coming,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.58,0:19:41.44,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,with its armies straight from hell
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.02,0:19:45.49,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Their black shadows threaten us all
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.50,0:19:49.19,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,but I'll fight to maintain\Nthe peace of our world!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.19,0:19:52.88,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Go! Go! Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.88,0:19:56.45,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,With my shining machine...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.45,0:19:59.98,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Rider Jump!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.98,0:20:03.44,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Rider Kick!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.44,0:20:07.20,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider, Kamen Rider
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.20,0:20:10.88,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Rider, Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.68,0:20:21.49,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Shocker is coming,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.49,0:20:25.04,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,with its armies made of demons
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.04,0:20:28.50,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Their black shadows\Nthreaten our friends,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.50,0:20:32.24,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,but I'll fight to maintain\Nthe peace of our world!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.24,0:20:35.72,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Go! Go! Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.72,0:20:39.33,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,With my scarf of red...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.33,0:20:42.98,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Rider Jump!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.98,0:20:46.64,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Rider Kick!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.64,0:20:50.23,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider, Kamen Rider
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.23,0:20:53.95,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Rider, Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.93,0:21:04.52,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Shocker is coming
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.52,0:21:08.22,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,with its armies spreading fear
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.22,0:21:11.85,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Their black shadows\Nthreaten our towns,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.85,0:21:15.42,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,but I'll fight to maintain\Nthe peace of our world!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.42,0:21:19.09,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Go! Go! Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.09,0:21:22.70,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,With my mask of green...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.70,0:21:26.28,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Rider Jump!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.28,0:21:29.78,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Rider Kick!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.78,0:21:33.68,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider, Kamen Rider
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.68,0:21:37.21,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Rider, Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.70,0:21:35.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Rider Drill Shoot!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.57,0:21:42.74,Default,,0,0,0,,My leader.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.13,0:21:44.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I must know...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.84,0:21:47.72,Default,,0,0,0,,You said the Kamen\NRider would not appear.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.64,0:21:51.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Why then, my leader...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.09,0:21:54.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Silence, Ambassador Hell.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.13,0:21:56.80,Default,,0,0,0,,The failures are all on your head.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.54,0:22:02.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Go on, look at the screen.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.85,0:22:06.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you know what that is?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.50,0:22:17.52,Default,,0,0,0,,A cyborg I've never seen before...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.54,0:22:20.75,Default,,0,0,0,,My leader.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.08,0:22:22.36,Default,,0,0,0,,What is the meaning of this?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.36,0:22:25.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I have no need to tell you.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.35,0:22:28.96,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.96,0:22:33.12,Default,,0,0,0,,If you drive me to it, then...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.24,0:22:48.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I swear to work hard as a member\Nof the Kamen Rider Kid Corps,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.37,0:22:49.86,Default,,0,0,0,,to uphold justice and peace.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.72,0:22:55.91,Default,,0,0,0,,We're counting on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.29,0:22:59.78,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The Shocker cyborg\NUnidogma was defeated,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.78,0:23:02.69,Narrator,,0,0,0,,but uncertainty hung heavy\Naround Hongo Takeshi.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.69,0:23:06.86,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Who was that powerful unknown\Nenemy that had appeared before him?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.03,0:23:10.84,Cont,,0,60,155,,{\blur.8\fad(0,400)}To be continued
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.99,0:23:13.83,NEP AND TITLE,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,0)\4aFF\bord0\b1\fs60\fnCalibri\pos(285.175,252.203)\c&HFFFFFF&}Next Episode Preview
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.91,0:23:20.77,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The rattle of a snake comes\Nfrom Ambassador Hell's body.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.77,0:23:24.66,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Glinting blue eyes pierce through Rider.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.66,0:23:31.03,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Stay tuned to this channel next week for\N"Ambassador Hell!! His Fearsome True Form?"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.07,0:23:31.03,NEP AND TITLE,,0,0,0,,{\fscx100\fs115\bord0.8\fnCienfuegos\4aFF\1c&HF3F4F4&\b1\pos(487.167,730.389)}Ambassador Hell!!\N His Fearsome True Form?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.15,0:23:50.54,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Kicking off the ground with a Rider Jump,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.54,0:23:57.96,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,a great turbine that\Nwhirls through the air!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.96,0:24:01.71,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Calling up lightning with a Rider Kick!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.71,0:24:05.53,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Striking down enemies with a Rider Chop!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.53,0:24:09.13,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Oh, oh Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.13,0:24:13.19,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider!
Comment: 0,0:01:19.97,0:01:24.94,Default,,0,0,0,,The Terrifying Unidogma\N+ Ghost Monsters